[
    {
        "text": "Here's how to record your computer screen",
        "start": 0.08,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "on Windows 10 and Mac.",
        "start": 2.04,
        "duration": 1.593
    },
    {
        "text": "Use the clickable sections below",
        "start": 4.53,
        "duration": 1.61
    },
    {
        "text": "to skip to your computer software.",
        "start": 6.14,
        "duration": 2.508
    },
    {
        "text": "You can record your screen on Windows 10",
        "start": 11.35,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "using the Game Bar app.",
        "start": 13.43,
        "duration": 1.453
    },
    {
        "text": "First, open whatever it is you'd like",
        "start": 15.84,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "to record on your PC.",
        "start": 18.16,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, open the Game Bar",
        "start": 20.29,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "by pressing the Windows key",
        "start": 21.79,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "and G on your keyboard.",
        "start": 23.68,
        "duration": 2.003
    },
    {
        "text": "If it doesn't open using the shortcut,",
        "start": 26.86,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "the Game Bar may not be enabled.",
        "start": 29.16,
        "duration": 1.923
    },
    {
        "text": "Search Game Bar settings,",
        "start": 31.92,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "and open the menu that appears.",
        "start": 33.45,
        "duration": 1.783
    },
    {
        "text": "In that menu,",
        "start": 36.73,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "toggle on the \"enable\nXbox Game Bar\" button.",
        "start": 38.08,
        "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Once the Game Bar is opened,",
        "start": 41.67,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "the recording tools will be",
        "start": 43.41,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "in the top left corner",
        "start": 44.59,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "in a window labeled \"Capture.\"",
        "start": 45.68,
        "duration": 1.773
    },
    {
        "text": "If the recording tools are not visible,",
        "start": 48.46,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "click the icon that\nlooks like a webcam here",
        "start": 50.7,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "to make them visible.",
        "start": 53.19,
        "duration": 1.073
    },
    {
        "text": "In the Capture window,",
        "start": 55.31,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "click the white circle icon here",
        "start": 56.78,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "to start your screen recording.",
        "start": 58.54,
        "duration": 1.683
    },
    {
        "text": "A small bar will appear",
        "start": 61.3,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "on the right-hand side of your screen",
        "start": 62.37,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "showing how long you've\nbeen screen-recording for.",
        "start": 64.01,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to record your own voice,",
        "start": 67.32,
        "duration": 2.17
    },
    {
        "text": "you can click the microphone icon here,",
        "start": 69.49,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "and it will start recording audio",
        "start": 72.16,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "from your default microphone.",
        "start": 73.66,
        "duration": 1.503
    },
    {
        "text": "Stop the recording by\nclicking the stop icon here.",
        "start": 76.0,
        "duration": 2.843
    },
    {
        "text": "You can find your new screen recordings",
        "start": 80.22,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "in your PC's videos\nfolder under \"Captures.\"",
        "start": 82.04,
        "duration": 4.05
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also find them",
        "start": 86.09,
        "duration": 0.99
    },
    {
        "text": "by opening the Game Bar",
        "start": 87.08,
        "duration": 1.61
    },
    {
        "text": "and clicking \"Show all captures.\"",
        "start": 88.69,
        "duration": 2.583
    },
    {
        "text": "You can record your screen on Mac",
        "start": 95.41,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "using a built-in QuickTime Player app.",
        "start": 97.03,
        "duration": 3.07
    },
    {
        "text": "First open \"QuickTime\nPlayer\" in applications.",
        "start": 100.1,
        "duration": 3.283
    },
    {
        "text": "Click \"File,\"",
        "start": 104.47,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "and then \"New Screen Recording.\"",
        "start": 105.83,
        "duration": 2.053
    },
    {
        "text": "Click \"Options\" in the\nscreenshot toolbar here",
        "start": 108.76,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "to adjust the screen size",
        "start": 111.2,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "and audio you want to record.",
        "start": 112.52,
        "duration": 1.563
    },
    {
        "text": "In the screenshot toolbar,",
        "start": 115.15,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "click this icon here to set the recording",
        "start": 117.02,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "to capture your entire screen.",
        "start": 119.35,
        "duration": 2.394
    },
    {
        "text": "To record a portion of the screen instead,",
        "start": 121.744,
        "duration": 2.366
    },
    {
        "text": "click the dash-line icon,",
        "start": 124.11,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "and then adjust the dotted line",
        "start": 126.06,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "to select the portion of the screen",
        "start": 127.46,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "you want to record.",
        "start": 128.93,
        "duration": 1.063
    },
    {
        "text": "Click the \"Record\" button\nto begin recording.",
        "start": 131.3,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "An icon will appear here",
        "start": 134.57,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "to show that the recording is underway.",
        "start": 136.14,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "To stop recording,",
        "start": 138.96,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "click the icon here.",
        "start": 140.11,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "QuickTime Player will open\nyour recording automatically.",
        "start": 142.24,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "You can save your\nrecording to any location",
        "start": 145.25,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "by choosing \"File,\" \"Save,\"",
        "start": 147.41,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "and then specifying your location.",
        "start": 150.69,
        "duration": 2.833
    }
]